description.plain: Lucenzo de son vrai nom Luis Filipe Fraga Oliveira, né le 27 mai 1983 à Bordeaux en Gironde, est un auteur-compositeur-interprète franco-portugais.

body.plain: Lucenzo de son vrai nom Luis Filipe Fraga Oliveira, né le 27 mai 1983 à Bordeaux en Gironde, est un auteur-compositeur-interprète franco-portugais.

description.plain:
The song was originally the Portuguese-French singer Lucenzo’s hit, called “Vem dançar kuduro”, featuring Big Ali. Reggaeton kingpin Don Omar remixed the song and made this track, spawning a massive hit

In the song, Don Omar raps in Spanish while Lucenzo’s verses are in his native Portuguese. When they speak to each other, they use English
